The evidence with the title 'Businesses claim Obamacare has forced them to cut employee hours ' says Aug 13, 2013  ...  ... Council Of Economic Advisors , said, “ we are seeing no systematic evidence that the Affordable Care Act is having an adverse impact on job growth or the number of hours employees are working . … [S]ince the ACA became law, nearly 90 percent of the gain in employment has been in full - time positions.”.
